    <li>Provide and improve SLNG services.</li>
    <li>Detect technical issues and maintain security.</li>
    <li>Service communications (e.g., updates, support).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell your personal data. Data may be shared with trusted service
    providers (e.g., analytics and crash reporting) only as necessary and with
    adequate safeguards.
  </p>

  <h2>Storage & Retention</h2>
  <p>
    Data is retained only as long as necessary for the purposes described. By
    default, input content is processed transiently. If you create saved lists
    (e.g., favorites/private dictionary), that data remains until you delete it
    or close your account.
  </p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>
    We implement reasonable technical and organizational safeguards to protect
    data, including encryption in transit and access minimization practices.
  </p>

